### 5.5 MATERIALS & SOURCING

**Fused Silica Inner Wall:**
- **Supplier:** Corning Advanced Optics
- **Product Code:** HPFS 7980 Premium Grade
- **Form:** Custom toroid (machined from blanks)
- **Machining:** Precision grinding + polishing
- **Surface Finish:** Ra < 0.5 nm (optical grade)
- **Lead Time:** 16-20 weeks
- **Cost:** $180,000 - $220,000

**Stainless Steel Outer Shell:**
- **Supplier:** ATI Allegheny Ludlum
- **Grade:** 316L (low carbon)
- **Form:** Rolled and welded sections
- **Heat Treatment:** Solution annealed
- **Surface:** Electropolished (Ra < 0.4 Î¼m)
- **Lead Time:** 8-12 weeks
- **Cost:** $45,000 - $65,000

**Vacuum Flanges:**
- **Supplier:** MDC Vacuum (Hositrad in Europe)
- **Type:** ConFlat (CF) copper gasket seal
- **Material:** 304 SS with OFHC copper gaskets
- **Leak Rate:** <10â»Â¹â° TorrÂ·L/s
