## SECTION 8: RF POWER & CONTROL SYSTEMS

### 8.1 POWER REQUIREMENTS SUMMARY

**Total System Power Budget:**

| Subsystem | Power (kW) | Notes |
|-----------|------------|-------|
| Plasma RF heating | 300 | 6Ã— 50kW generators |
| Emitter array | 315 | 105 emitters @ 2kW each |
| Toroidal field coils | 0* | Superconducting (reactive) |
