- **Wormhole nucleation:** +500 kW (250 ms burst)
- **Peak total:** 1.95 MW

**Facility Requirements:**
- **Service:** 2.5 MW @ 480V 3-phase
- **Backup:** 500 kW diesel generator (critical loads only)

