### 8.3 UNINTERRUPTIBLE POWER SUPPLY (UPS)

**Critical Loads (Must Not Lose Power):**
- Control computers
- Synchronization systems
- Plasma shutdown controls
- Emergency vacuum valves

**UPS Specifications:**
- **Capacity:** 100 kVA / 80 kW
- **Runtime:** 15 minutes (battery)
- **Type:** Online double-conversion
- **Batteries:** VRLA (valve-regulated lead-acid)
- **Manufacturer:** Eaton 9395 or APC Symmetra
- **Cost:** ~$65,000

**Backup Generator:**
- **Capacity:** 500 kW prime power
- **Fuel:** Diesel (1000 gallon tank, 48 hr runtime)
- **Auto-start:** <10 seconds
- **Manufacturer:** Caterpillar or Cummins
- **Cost:** ~$125,000 (including installation)

